title: IRS Announces Key Milestone in FATCA Implementation; U.S. Begins Reciprocal Automatic Exchange of Tax Information ...
text: ( Source : IRS - Internal Revenue Service ) WASHINGTON - The Internal Revenue Service today announced the exchange of financial account information with certain foreign tax administrations, meeting a key Sept . 30 milestone related to FATCA,
